Service Availability
====================

[Archive-It](https://archive-it.org/) and [blog.archive.org](https://blog.archive.org/) resumed.

Other Internet Archive services are temporarily offline.

Please come to our event this week: Escaping the Memory Hole [Wednesday, October 23rd](https://blog.archive.org/event/escaping-the-memory-hole/).

Please check our official accounts, including [Twitter/X](https://twitter.com/internetarchive/), [Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:73dpznbu4wqwtcyurwbiulov) or [Mastodon](https://mastodon.archive.org/deck/@internetarchive) for the latest information.

Our patrons have asked how they can support: [PayPal](https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/internetarchive).

We apologize for the inconvenience.
